{"tid":803325,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[又炒車]日本人最愛壽司排行榜,三文魚壽司排第六","createTime":"2018-09-02T07:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T09:49:15.000Z","uid":48631,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0005cc7911b6bc3daeb595b09b7a6ed826e8b8f6","tid":803325,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:39:09.000Z","msg":"日本傳媒調查讀者最喜愛的壽司款式，發現日人最愛的是「中拖羅」(吞拿魚中腹肉)，其次是赤身（吞拿魚背）壽司，不過第三位竟然是墨魚，壓倒海膽和三文魚，讓不少日人也感到意外。<br />\n<br />\n《朝日新聞》以問卷形式訪問1479名電子版會員，選出「最喜愛的壽司配料」調查讀者最愛的壽司口味，結果吞拿魚佔據首兩名位置，受訪的72歲群馬縣男子更形容︰「中拖羅是壽司之王」。<br />\n<br />\n排第三名的是墨魚壽司，68歲作家佐川芳枝表示︰「雖然我也喜歡那股嚼勁，不過第三名還真讓人吃驚。」在東京經營壽司店的她「教路」，加鹽及青檸享用更為美味。第四位是屬於高級食材的海膽壽司，可能因為不少人怕腥味不敢吃，而影響了海膽壽司的受歡迎程度，而第五位是星鰻(穴子)壽司。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港人最為熟識的三文魚壽司排行第六位，報道指日本在江戶時代出現的壽司，並沒包括三文魚，日本的三文魚大部份是國外產的養殖魚，所以有部份堅持使用國產魚的壽司店並不提供三文魚。</span><br />\n<br />\n「最喜愛壽司」排行榜<br />\n<br />\n1 吞拿魚（中拖羅） 789票<br />\n2 吞拿魚（赤身）751票<br />\n3 墨魚 709票<br />\n4 海膽 684票<br />\n5 星鰻 667票<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6 三文魚 621票</span><br />\n7 甜蝦 609票<br />\n8 油甘魚 587票<br />\n9 帶子 573票<br />\n10 三文魚籽 570票<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個班成日話冇日本人食三文魚嘅child登仔點解釋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫你地諗埋,傳統壽司店唔會有三文魚壽司,有三文魚食嘅舖頭唔算數<br />\n訪問得個千幾,代表唔到成個日本,冇參考價值<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180902/58632874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58632874&d=%2FGfR7hlU0oN0UP%2BRcjWjXTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=4fa6ea50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58632874&h=a98f6f59\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180902/58632874</a>"},{"pid":"618845de365e53167a43238fb372ad957a071a1b","tid":803325,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"諗多個解釋,投三文魚個班都係居日港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d490b6b0023c467bb85746ec3ee4bbae2f349573","tid":803325,"uid":36296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"蔡欄：日本人係唔食....."},{"pid":"8dc35bcd98a28670e3c0fab849d5b71ecd9b1e93","tid":803325,"uid":74933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"堅持用國產魚既店冇 <br />\n係因為日本產既三文魚都係唔適合生食<br />\n所以原先日本人係唔會食<br />\n暫時係娜威三文魚生食係比較安全"},{"pid":"a688fd339194249e736da180c2d7f49853a58709","tid":803325,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:02:48.000Z","msg":"香港好食既拖羅邊到搵"},{"pid":"cda6b7b0332a83f6047b1fc7f4c9a7b2c9338f72","tid":803325,"uid":96651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"估唔到墨魚上榜<br />\n墨魚本身味淡 口感又奇怪"},{"pid":"7478acf65546014a28a55cdf8ec250375879a549","tid":803325,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"日本人只食頭五名，第六及打後一律唔食"},{"pid":"e8728dd5e105263bd16975649a3f96401abd80ba","tid":803325,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"大拖羅連榜都唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850d4d81414519946c862c0aec39c1a00885fa14","tid":803325,"uid":5546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8728dd5e105263bd16975649a3f96401abd80ba","tid":803325,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"大拖羅連榜都唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"可能太肥<br />\n中拖羅啱啱好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b29f64d4fce0